<refentry xml:id="vtiful-kernel-excel.insertImageOpt" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
 <refnamediv>
  <refname>Vtiful\Kernel\Excel::insertImageOpt</refname>
  <refpurpose>Vtiful\Kernel\Excel insertImageOpt</refpurpose>
 </refnamediv>
 <refsect1 role="description">
  &reftitle.description;
  <methodsynopsis>
   <modifier>public</modifier> <type>Vtiful\Kernel\Excel</type> <methodname>Vtiful\Kernel\Excel::insertImageOpt</methodname>
   <methodparam><type>int</type><parameter>row</parameter></methodparam>
   <methodparam><type>int</type><parameter>column</parameter></methodparam>
   <methodparam><type>string</type><parameter>image</parameter></methodparam>
   <methodparam><type>array</type><parameter>options</parameter></methodparam>
  </methodsynopsis>
  <simpara>Inserts a local image into the given cell with additional placement options such as offsets, scaling, alternative text and an optional hyperlink.</simpara>
 </refsect1>
 <refsect1 role="parameters">
  &reftitle.parameters;
  <variablelist>
   <varlistentry>
    <term><parameter>row</parameter></term>
    <listitem>
     <simpara>The cell row, zero-based.</simpara>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term><parameter>column</parameter></term>
    <listitem>
     <simpara>The cell column, zero-based.</simpara>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term><parameter>image</parameter></term>
    <listitem>
     <simpara>The local image path.</simpara>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term><parameter>options</parameter></term>
    <listitem>
     <simpara>An array of placement options. Recognised keys are <literal>x_offset</literal> and <literal>y_offset</literal> (int, pixels from the top-left of the anchor cell), <literal>x_scale</literal> and <literal>y_scale</literal> (float, scale factor), <literal>description</literal> (string, alternative text), <literal>decorative</literal> (bool), <literal>url</literal> and <literal>tip</literal> (string, hyperlink and tooltip) and <literal>object_position</literal> (int).</simpara>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
 </refsect1>
 <refsect1 role="returnvalues">
  &reftitle.returnvalues;
  <simpara>Returns the current <classname>Vtiful\Kernel\Excel</classname> instance.</simpara>
 </refsect1>
</refentry>
